## Route Names

**RESTful resource names (plural):**

```ruby
# config/routes.rb

# Good: Plural resource names
resources :articles
resources :users
resources :blog_posts

# Custom routes: snake_case
get '/about_us', to: 'pages#about'
get '/contact_form', to: 'pages#contact'

# Named routes: snake_case with _path/_url suffix
# articles_path → /articles
# article_path(@article) → /articles/:id
# new_article_path → /articles/new
# edit_article_path(@article) → /articles/:id/edit
```
